, \"from\": 1129, \"to\": 1135}]}, {\"sentence\": \"), and numerous breakout stars for Team USA, which won more medals (126) than any country and tied for the gold-medal lead (40).\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1318, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1225, \"end\": 1233, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9986991508358763, \"rank\": 0.0013025435452741587, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"), and numerous breakout stars\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1220}, {\"ngram\": \"more medals\", \"from\": 1245, \"to\": 1256}, {\"ngram\": \"any country\", \"from\": 1268, \"to\": 1279}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold-medal lead\", \"from\": 1293, \"to\": 1312}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The world's biggest media event, the Paris Olympics was consumed in massive numbers on NBCU platforms.\", \"from\": 1322, \"to\": 1424, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1409, \"end\": 1413, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBCU\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The world's biggest media event\", \"from\": 1322, \"to\": 1353}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 1355, \"to\": 1373}, {\"ngram\": \"massive numbers\", \"from\": 1390, \"to\": 1405}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Highlights include: Mark Lazarus, Chairman, NBCUniversal Media Group:\\\"Our NBCUniversal team matched the occasion of this transformative Paris Olympics, presenting peerless coverage in daytime and primetime across all platforms, including the NBC broadcast network, which once again was home to the most-watched night of television for 17 consecutive days.\", \"from\": 1425, \"to\": 1789, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1454, \"end\": 1466, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_Lazarus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mark Lazarus\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_Lazarus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_Lazarus\"}, {\"begin\": 1478, \"end\": 1490, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.865145521475687e-14, \"text\": \"NBCUniversal\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}, {\"begin\": 1676, \"end\": 1679, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9999993373250995, \"rank\": 6.566848889391158e-07, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Highlights\", \"from\": 1425, \"to\": 1435}, {\"ngram\": \"the occasion\", \"from\": 1525, \"to\": 1537}, {\"ngram\": \"this transformative Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 1541, \"to\": 1575}, {\"ngram\": \"peerless coverage\", \"from\": 1588, \"to\": 1605}, {\"ngram\": \"daytime\", \"from\": 1609, \"to\": 1616}, {\"ngram\": \"all platforms\", \"from\": 1638, \"to\": 1651}, {\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 1711, \"to\": 1715}, {\"ngram\": \"the most-watched night\", \"from\": 1719, \"to\": 1741}, {\"ngram\": \"television\", \"from\": 1745, \"to\": 1755}, {\"ngram\": \"17 consecutive days\", \"from\": 1760, \"to\": 1779}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Games marked a groundbreaking moment for Peacock, which delivered a flawless user experience and cutting-edge innovation while shattering all-time Olympics streaming records.\", \"from\": 1790, \"to\": 1968, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1835, \"end\": 1842, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"score\": 0.9999999948631739, \"rank\": 5.