soaring local news ratings.\", \"from\": 2140, \"to\": 2287, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2140, \"end\": 2148, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 6.155778542746809e-13, \"text\": \"NBC News\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}, {\"begin\": 2179, \"end\": 2184, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9504412309647736e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"location\", \"from\": 2167, \"to\": 2175}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 2199, \"to\": 2214}, {\"ngram\": \"our owned-stations\", \"from\": 2222, \"to\": 2240}, {\"ngram\": \"affiliates\", \"from\": 2245, \"to\": 2255}, {\"ngram\": \"local news ratings\", \"from\": 2268, \"to\": 2286}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We sold more advertising for the Paris Olympics than for any other Games, and we delivered for all of our partners.\", \"from\": 2288, \"to\": 2403, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more advertising\", \"from\": 2296, \"to\": 2312}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 2317, \"to\": 2335}, {\"ngram\": \"any other Games\", \"from\": 2345, \"to\": 2360}, {\"ngram\": \"our partners\", \"from\": 2390, \"to\": 2402}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Parks and Studios received unmatched promotion, as the 'halo effect' boosted all of our businesses.\", \"from\": 2404, \"to\": 2503, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Parks\", \"from\": 2404, \"to\": 2409}, {\"ngram\": \"Studios\", \"from\": 2414, \"to\": 2421}, {\"ngram\": \"unmatched promotion\", \"from\": 2431, \"to\": 2450}, {\"ngram\": \"the 'halo effect\", \"from\": 2455, \"to\": 2471}, {\"ngram\": \"our businesses\", \"from\": 2488, \"to\": 2502}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris Olympics was as exciting as we could have hoped, and we can not wait to work with our partners at the IOC and USOPC in Milan-Cortina in '26 and LA28.\\\"\", \"from\": 2504, \"to\": 2664, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2616, \"end\": 2619, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9277267646625204e-30, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 2504, \"to\": 2522}, {\"ngram\": \"our partners\", \"from\": 2596, \"to\": 2608}, {\"ngram\": \"USOPC\", \"from\": 2624, \"to\": 2629}, {\"ngram\": \"Milan-Cortina\", \"from\": 2633, \"to\": 2646}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rick Cordella, President, NBC Sports:\\\"From the Opening Ceremony procession down the River Seine through more than two weeks of heart-stopping competition culminating this past weekend with Team USA's gold rush in men's and women's basketball, women's soccer, and track & field relays, these Olympics have captivated Americans in huge numbers across NBCUniversal platforms.\", \"from\": 2666, \"to\": 3038, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2671, \"end\": 2679, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Albion_(Blake)\", \"score\": 0.992684896232193, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cordella\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Albion_(Blake)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Albion_(Blake)\"}, {\"begin\": 2692, \"end\": 2702, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.969832488992244, \"rank\": 0.031056924288633003, \"text\": \"NBC Sports\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}, {\"begin\": 2750, \"end\": 2761, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"River Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}, {\"begin\": 2855, \"end\": 2863, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9986991508358763, \"rank\": 0.0013025435452741587, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 3015, \"end\": 3027, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.865145521475687e-14, \"text\": \"NBCUniversal\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"President\", \"from\": 2681, \"to\": 2690}, {\"ngram\": \"the Opening Ceremony procession\", \"from\": 2709, \"to\": 2740}, {\"ngram\": \"more than two weeks\", \"from\": 2770, \"to\": 2789}, {\"ngram\": \"heart-stopping competition\", \"from\": 2793, \"to\": 2819}, {\"ngram\": \"men's and women's basketball\", \"from\": 2879, \"to\": 2907}, {\"ngram\": \"women's soccer\", \"from\": 2909, \"to\": 2923}, {\"ngram\": \"track & field relays\", \"from\": 2929, \"to\": 2949}, {\"ngram\": \"these Olympics\", \"from\": 2951, \"to\": 2965}, {\"ngram\": \"Americans\", \"from\": 2982, \"to\": 2991}, {\"ngram\": \"huge numbers\", \"from\": 2995, \"to\": 3007}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Led by our best-in-class engineering and production teams in Paris and Stamford, a staff of more than 3,000 worked tirelessly to present these reimagined Games in new and innovative ways in all dayparts and on all platforms.\", \"from\": 3039, \"to\": 3263, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3100, \"end\": 3105, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9504412309647736e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486